\end{equation}

The least coefficient of friction for the cylinder to roll down without slipping is obtained by setting \( a_R = a_s \):

\begin{align*}
    2 \mu g \cos \theta &= g (\sin \theta - \mu \cos \theta) \\
    \Rightarrow \mu &= \frac{1}{3} \tan \theta
\end{align*}

